Edit Document data

 

To edit the Document select the Edit button

The Documents open in Edit mode. In Edit mode of the Document you can:

  1. Write the report
  2. Add additional sections and text at the landing page 
  3. Format the free text by using the document formatting controls at the top of the page or add additional widgets to present additional data in the selected tab

1. Change the heading style of the font
2. Change the fond of the text
3. Change the size of the text
4. Line spacing
5. Change the text to Bold, Italic or Strikethrough (the Strikethrough menu opens to more options)
6. Change the text color and highlight it.
7. Add a number list or bullet list
8. Add a table
9. Add page break
10. Add Info section
11. Add layout
12. Insert and configure widget
13. Ads internal and external links

 

Once opened for editing the Document becomes locked for editing by other system users. All other user will be able to edit the Documents when you save the Document.

        4. There are two save options:

  • The Save & Edit options saves the changes and the document stays in the Edit mode.
  • By using the Save button document is saved. Document is opened in Preview mode,
